data.thought: S33|H|S32|Educational Phenotype F1: 'Socratic Tutor'. Notebook presents programming challenge. Instead of showing answer, uses Thoughtbox to ask leading questions. Tracks learner responses. Branches based on misconceptions detected. Observable: question tree, learner path, mastery indicators. Container runs learner's attempts, provides feedback. AI never gives direct answer - guides discovery. Use case: CS education, bootcamps, self-paced learning.
